    <abstract>
      <t>The purpose of this document is to form a basis for discussion about the development of the Mobile IP standard. It is foreseen that cellular mobile systems will give rise to a widespread global use of IP mobility tunnels. We describe scenarios and identify important issues for the Mobile IP specification and the proposed DIAMETER extensions for Mobile IP.</t>
